Photo by Moon Omens on September 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Every impulse in you wants to react, but you choose to find calmness before creating the next moment. You choose to find yourself instead of giving in to someone else's frequency. You choose to respond much differently than you used to.'.

Photo by Moon Omens on September 14, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'You stop beating yourself up fo looping back into past patterns. Instead, you appreciate that your weakness has become clear to you, so you can move forward with more wisdom.'.
Photo by Moon Omens on September 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'You're learning to stop minimizing yourself 1n order to keep the peace and remain comfortable where you are.'.

Photo by Moon Omens on September 14, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'You allow your heart your passion, your gut feelings and the signs you get along the way to lead your life rather than letting your and past traumas lead you. pain'.

May be an image of text that says 'You value solitude and are learning to to give yourself space to connect with your emotions and deeper feelings In doing this, you learn that your inner light is actively trying to shed light on your perspective through aha moments, goose bumps, and through subtle feelings fjoy and clarity'.
Photo by Moon Omens on September 14, 2021. May be an image of text.

Photo shared by Moon Omens on September 14, 2021 tagging @moonomens, and @carriemariebush. May be an image of text that says 'The entire Universe is working for you.
